  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: bug-bounty\r\n*Summary*: on screen 'Confirm password' after typing wrong Password and appearing 'Password confirmation doesn't match password' is shows even you fix value in input field until you tap on 'Next'\r\n![password](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/37445509-286734c2-2821-11e8-80b3-cfb32408fce3.png) \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n'Password confirmation doesn't match password' disappears when you start to fix value in 'confirm password' field\r\n* Note: expected behavior is based on experience with https://google.com\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n'Password confirmation doesn't match password' doesn't disappear even when you entered correct value in 'confirm password' field\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Tap on 'Create new account'\r\n- Enter password, proceed to Confirm password\r\n- Enter wrong password in 'Confirm password' field\r\n- Fix value in  'Confirm password' field\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version:  Nightly build for March 15 (https://status-im.github.io/nightly/)\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n* Video: http://take.ms/Jz0wxo",
